# https://leetcode.com/problems/build-a-matrix-with-conditions/description/

i want to build a grid.

i want to fill the grid with numbers.

where the numbers would be on the grid is not known.
it is described.

every number can tell you one of two things:
* it's vertical info
* it's horizontal info

it's vertical info tells you:
    what number comes above it, and
    what number comes beneath it

it's horizontal info tells you:
    what number comes before it, and
    what number comes after it

so, what's the first step?


